---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Deploy - a10y" description="Deploy a10y on Kubernetes (Helm) or Docker Compose for local development.">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Deploy</h1>
        <p class="lead">a10y runs on Kubernetes (production) or Docker Compose (local development).</p>

        <!-- Architecture overview -->
        <h2>Architecture</h2>
        <div class="arch">
            <div class="arch-row">
                <div class="arch-box ui">
                    <div class="label">UI</div>
                    <span>aether-ide</span>
                    <span>aether-term</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-row">
                <div class="arch-box core">
                    <div class="label">Core</div>
                    <span>correlation-engine</span>
                    <span>active-inventory</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-row">
                <div class="arch-box infra">
                    <div class="label">Data</div>
                    <span>OpenObserve</span>
                    <span>Keep</span>
                    <span>Qdrant</span>
                    <span>Vector</span>
                    <span>NATS</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dashboards -->
        <h2>Dashboards (Data Layer UIs)</h2>
        <p>After deployment, the Data Layer components provide built-in dashboards out of the box. These are the primary interfaces for day-to-day operations.</p>

        <div class="dash-grid">
            <div class="dash-card">
                <div class="dash-header">
                    <h3>OpenObserve</h3>
                    <span class="dash-port">:5080</span>
                </div>
                <p>Logs, metrics, traces — all in one UI. Build dashboards, run SQL/PromQL queries, set up alerts. The primary observability interface.</p>
                <div class="dash-cred">
                    <code>admin@a10y.local</code> / <code>changeme</code>
                </div>
                <div class="dash-url"><code>http://localhost:5080</code></div>
            </div>
            <div class="dash-card">
                <div class="dash-header">
                    <h3>Keep</h3>
                    <span class="dash-port">:3001</span>
                </div>
                <p>Alert management console. View correlated alerts, create workflows, configure integrations with external monitoring tools.</p>
                <div class="dash-url"><code>http://localhost:3001</code></div>
            </div>
            <div class="dash-card">
                <div class="dash-header">
                    <h3>Qdrant</h3>
                    <span class="dash-port">:6333/dashboard</span>
                </div>
                <p>Vector DB dashboard. Browse collections, inspect stored embeddings, run similarity searches, monitor cluster health.</p>
                <div class="dash-url"><code>http://localhost:6333/dashboard</code></div>
            </div>
            <div class="dash-card">
                <div class="dash-header">
                    <h3>NATS Monitor</h3>
                    <span class="dash-port">:8222</span>
                </div>
                <p>Messaging health. Active connections, JetStream streams/consumers, message rates, subscription details.</p>
                <div class="dash-url"><code>http://localhost:8222</code></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="port-table">
            <h3>All Ports</h3>
            <table>
                <tr><th>Service</th><th>Port</th><th>Role</th><th>UI</th></tr>
                <tr><td>OpenObserve</td><td>5080</td><td>Logs, metrics, traces</td><td>Dashboard</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Keep (frontend)</td><td>3001</td><td>Alert management</td><td>Dashboard</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Keep (backend)</td><td>8082</td><td>Alert API</td><td>—</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Qdrant</td><td>6333</td><td>Vector DB</td><td>Dashboard</td></tr>
                <tr><td>NATS</td><td>4222 / 8222</td><td>Messaging / Monitor</td><td>Monitor</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Vector</td><td>9000 / 6514</td><td>Syslog / Vector protocol</td><td>—</td></tr>
                <tr><td>correlation-engine</td><td>8000</td><td>AI engine API</td><td>—</td></tr>
                <tr><td>active-inventory</td><td>8081</td><td>Topology API</td><td>—</td></tr>
                <tr><td>aether-ide</td><td>8080</td><td>Web IDE (planned)</td><td>—</td></tr>
                <tr><td>aether-term</td><td>3000</td><td>Terminal (planned)</td><td>—</td></tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <!-- Kubernetes -->
        <h2>Kubernetes (Helm)</h2>

        <h3>Prerequisites</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Kubernetes 1.28+</li>
            <li>Helm 3.12+</li>
            <li>Storage class with dynamic provisioning (for OpenObserve, Qdrant)</li>
            <li>Anthropic API key (for correlation-engine)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Quick Start</h3>
        <pre><code># Add the a10y chart repo
helm repo add a10y https://autonomously-io.github.io/charts
helm repo update

# Create namespace and secret
kubectl create namespace a10y
kubectl -n a10y create secret generic correlation-engine-secrets \
  --from-literal=ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Install
helm install a10y a10y/autonomously -n a10y</code></pre>

        <h3>Custom Values</h3>
        <pre><code># values-prod.yaml
components:
  correlation-engine:
    env:
      AI_MODEL: "claude-sonnet-4-20250514"
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: "1"
        memory: 2Gi

  aether-ide:
    ingress:
      enabled: true
      host: ide.a10y.example.com

openobserve:
  auth:
    ZO_ROOT_USER_EMAIL: "admin@example.com"
    ZO_ROOT_USER_PASSWORD: "your-secure-password"
  persistence:
    size: 500Gi

qdrant:
  persistence:
    size: 50Gi

# Install with custom values
# helm install a10y a10y/autonomously -n a10y -f values-prod.yaml</code></pre>

        <h3>Disable Components</h3>
        <pre><code># Minimal install (engine + data layer only, no UI)
helm install a10y a10y/autonomously -n a10y \
  --set components.aether-ide.enabled=false \
  --set components.aether-term.enabled=false</code></pre>

        <!-- Docker Compose -->
        <h2>Docker Compose</h2>

        <h3>Prerequisites</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Docker 24+ &amp; Docker Compose v2</li>
            <li>8 GB+ RAM available</li>
            <li>Anthropic API key</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Setup</h3>
        <pre><code># Clone
git clone https://github.com/autonomously-io/autonomously-io.github.io.git a10y
cd a10y

# Configure
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env and set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY

# Start all services
docker compose up -d

# Check status
docker compose ps

# View logs
docker compose logs -f correlation-engine</code></pre>

        <h3>docker-compose.yml</h3>
        <pre><code>services:
  # -- Core
  correlation-engine:
    image: ghcr.io/autonomously-io/correlation-engine:latest
    ports: ["8000:8000"]
    environment:
      AI_MODEL: claude-sonnet-4-20250514
      OPENOBSERVE_URL: http://openobserve:5080
      OPENOBSERVE_USER: admin@a10y.local
      KEEP_API_URL: http://keep-backend:8080
      NATS_URL: nats://nats:4222
      QDRANT_URL: http://qdrant:6333
      QDRANT_COLLECTION: incidents
      INVENTORY_URL: http://active-inventory:8080
      ANTHROPIC_API_KEY: $&#123;ANTHROPIC_API_KEY&#125;
    depends_on: [openobserve, keep-backend, nats, qdrant]

  active-inventory:
    image: ghcr.io/autonomously-io/active-inventory:latest
    ports: ["8081:8080"]

  # -- UI
  aether-ide:
    image: ghcr.io/autonomously-io/aether-ide:latest
    ports: ["8080:8080"]
    environment:
      CORRELATION_ENGINE_URL: http://correlation-engine:8000

  aether-term:
    image: ghcr.io/autonomously-io/aether-term:latest
    ports: ["3000:3000"]
    environment:
      CORRELATION_ENGINE_URL: http://correlation-engine:8000

  # -- Data layer
  openobserve:
    image: public.ecr.aws/zinclabs/openobserve:latest
    ports: ["5080:5080"]
    environment:
      ZO_ROOT_USER_EMAIL: admin@a10y.local
      ZO_ROOT_USER_PASSWORD: changeme
      ZO_LOCAL_MODE: "true"
    volumes: ["openobserve-data:/data"]

  keep-backend:
    image: us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/keephq/keep/keep-api:latest
    ports: ["8082:8080"]

  keep-frontend:
    image: us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/keephq/keep/keep-ui:latest
    ports: ["3001:3000"]
    environment:
      API_URL: http://keep-backend:8080

  nats:
    image: nats:2-alpine
    ports: ["4222:4222", "8222:8222"]
    command: ["--js", "--sd", "/data", "-m", "8222"]
    volumes: ["nats-data:/data"]

  qdrant:
    image: qdrant/qdrant:latest
    ports: ["6333:6333"]
    volumes: ["qdrant-data:/qdrant/storage"]

  vector:
    image: timberio/vector:0.41.1-alpine
    ports: ["9000:9000", "6514:6514"]
    volumes: ["./vector.yaml:/etc/vector/vector.yaml:ro"]
    depends_on: [openobserve]

volumes:
  openobserve-data:
  nats-data:
  qdrant-data:</code></pre>

        <h3>.env.example</h3>
        <pre><code>ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here</code></pre>

        <!-- Log forwarding -->
        <h2>Log Forwarding</h2>
        <p>a10y ingests logs via Vector. Two input protocols are supported:</p>

        <div class="forward-grid">
            <div class="forward-card">
                <h3>Syslog (TCP :9000)</h3>
                <p>Send syslog from network devices, perfSONAR, etc.</p>
                <pre><code># rsyslog
*.* @@vector-host:9000

# syslog-ng
destination d_a10y &#123;
  tcp("vector-host" port(9000));
&#125;;</code></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="forward-card">
                <h3>Vector Protocol (:6514)</h3>
                <p>Deploy Vector agent on hosts to forward structured logs.</p>
                <pre><code># vector.yaml (agent)
sinks:
  a10y:
    type: vector
    address: "vector-host:6514"
    version: "2"</code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h3>Supported Sources</h3>
        <table>
            <tr><th>Source</th><th>Protocol</th><th>Transform</th></tr>
            <tr><td>free5GC</td><td>Vector agent</td><td>parse_free5gc (auto-tagged)</td></tr>
            <tr><td>perfSONAR</td><td>Syslog TCP</td><td>parse_perfsonar (auto-tagged)</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Network devices</td><td>Syslog TCP</td><td>Custom VRL transforms</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Kubernetes</td><td>Vector agent</td><td>Pod metadata enrichment</td></tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</Base>

<style>
    .arch {
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.4rem;
    }
    .arch-row {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }
    .arch-box {
        border: 1px solid #222;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        background: #0c0c0c;
    }
    .arch-box .label {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: #4a9eff;
        font-weight: 600;
        min-width: 40px;
    }
    .arch-box span {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #aaa;
    }
    .arch-box.core { border-color: #1a3a5c; }

    .port-table { margin: 1rem 0; }
    .port-table table { font-size: 0.9rem; }

    ul {
        margin: 0.8rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;
        color: #aaa;
    }
    li {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    pre {
        background: #111;
        border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
        margin: 0.8rem 0 1.5rem;
    }
    code {
        font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', 'Cascadia Code', monospace;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #ccc;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .forward-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
    }
    .forward-card {
        border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 1.2rem;
        background: #0c0c0c;
    }
    .forward-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    .forward-card p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .forward-card pre {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .dash-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 0.8rem;
        margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .dash-card {
        border: 1px solid #1a3a5c;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 1.2rem;
        background: #0c0c0c;
    }
    .dash-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .dash-header h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    .dash-port {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #666;
        font-family: monospace;
    }
    .dash-card p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .dash-cred {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #888;
        margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
    .dash-cred code {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        background: #151515;
        padding: 0.1rem 0.3rem;
        border-radius: 3px;
    }
    .dash-url code {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #4a9eff;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .forward-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .dash-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
</style>
